full_text: Part 9. Memberships and organizations. A. List your present and past membership in or affiliation with every organization, association, fund, foundation party, club, society, or similar group in the United States or in any other place. Include any military service III this part. If none, write "none". Include the name of organization, location, dates of membership and the nature of the organization.
